entries.journal_entry_description: You've started working for Borvo the Hutt on Naboo, the most notorious criminal on the planet.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: I'm going to the last place the snitch, Frangee, was seen. I hope he's still around there somewhere.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: I've got to find Frangee and make sure he doesn't report to his bosses.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Now that I've dealt with Frangee I'm going to go back and see Borvo's Guard.
